# HingeCraft Global Repository Structure

## Core Directories
- src/backend/ - Backend Velo functions
- public/pages/ - Frontend HTML pages
- docs/ - All documentation organized by category
- scripts/ - All scripts organized by purpose
- legal-pages/ - Legal page HTML files
- database/ - Database schemas and migrations

## Documentation Organization
- docs/deployment/ - Deployment guides
- docs/database/ - Database documentation
- docs/api/ - API integration docs
- docs/troubleshooting/ - Troubleshooting guides
- docs/guides/ - User guides
- docs/reference/ - Quick reference docs

## Archive
- archive/old-docs/ - Old/duplicate documentation
- archive/old-scripts/ - Old/duplicate scripts
